{"tid":1357104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未Fact Check 集中討論區","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:27:29.000Z","uid":5271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a858c7a1f3da139a72bc402a020059d997fea68","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"由於三毛情況嚴重，想大家合作一下<br />\n為免減少冇用Post 泛濫、造成不必要恐慌<br />\n以令有用Post 上熱門<br />\n<br />\n開新Post 前先檢查內容是否：<br />\n1. 二手Source 或未Fact check 資訊<br />\n(親戚朋友來源均為二手資料)<br />\n2. 以偏概全，斷章取義<br />\n3. 自製白色恐佈<br />\n4. 標題黨<br />\n5. 重覆Post <br />\n<br />\n**未Fact Check 資訊請在此Post 留言討論**<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n疑似XXX<br />\n黑幫大佬XXX <br />\n何君堯XXX<br />\nXXX 錄音流出<br />\n<br />\n想熱門Post 變返簡潔整齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08585bbccc7efb193f661c63f98294f71aeb70bf","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c55e61f16aa873faa80413cf47f469b097f782","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b6d6a4c4dc3afcbb51069b915a863867c8dffc","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b152c0b90baa50865681dc27614ffbc0295eb7","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"8753710932f721e43adf2607c0bab62f6cb8c360","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6879c00b0b3e7ffaa19879f5e2a749b8150fe1e0","tid":1357104,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike"